          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our journey begins from the ground up.</p><p>In 2024, Mono.M was born from a spark of inspiration in a chemistry lab—the first place founder Jill visited upon returning to school after 12 years in marketing. As she watched molecules react and transform, she envisioned a brand where science and artistry would intertwine to bring her dreams to life.</p><p>At Mono.M, we believe every life is a cinematic journey—filled with moments of joy, celebration, and inspiration. Each story is a beautiful memory worth preserving, and our fragrances are crafted to do just that. Through curiosity, empathy, and meticulous craftsmanship, we transform these stories into poetic scents, designed to be savored slowly in the sanctuary of your home.</p>",
